modules.description: This module supports creating, parsing, and serializing HTTP cookies and `Set-Cookie` headers per RFC 6265, handling attributes like `path`, `domain`, `expires`, `max_age`, and security flags (`secure`, `http_only`, `same_site`). It operates on `Http_cookie.t` records and string header representations, with utilities for validating cookie properties, comparing timestamps, and formatting dates per RFC 1123. Typical use cases include constructing response headers with session cookies, parsing incoming request cookies, and securely managing cookie expiration or attribute updates.
